entry.title: WEATHER ADVISORY , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 07:11 AM EST Tuesday 28 February 2023

entry.title: Tuesday: Light snow. High plus 1.
entry.summary: Light snow ending late this morning then cloudy with 30 percent chance of flurries. Clearing this afternoon. Amount 2 cm. Wind becoming west 30 km/h gusting to 50 late this morning. High plus 1. Wind chill minus 12 this morning. UV index 2 or low. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EST Tuesday 28 February 2023

entry.title: Tuesday night: A few clouds. Low minus 8.
entry.summary: Clear. Becoming partly cloudy after midnight. Wind west 20 km/h gusting to 40 becoming light this evening. Low minus 8. Wind chill minus 7 this evening and minus 12 overnight. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EST Tuesday 28 February 2023
